zh-Hans.consumables_main_brush_description: 主刷是机器人的主要清扫部件，胶毛一体的主刷以高速旋转卷起垃圾进入尘盒。但是随着工作时间的增长主刷会有磨损，影响清扫效果。建议工作300小时或更短时间更换一次。
zh-Hans.consumables_side_brush_description: 边刷用于清扫墙角垃圾，以黄金倾角接触地面将垃圾送入主刷。但是随着工作时间的增长边刷会有磨损，影响清扫效果。建议工作200小时或更短时间更换一次。
zh-Hans.consumables_filter_description: 可水洗滤网由高分子纤维组成，用于防止吸入尘盒的灰尘逸出。但工作一段时间后滤网可能会被堵塞,建议每两周用清水清洗一次，工作150小时或更短时间更换一次滤网。
zh-Hans.consumables_mop_description: 拖布是机器人进入拖地模式中的主要部件，是由超细纤维组成，吸水强、摩擦力大。但随着工作时间的增加和反复的清洗，拖布的纤维会有磨损或脱落，建议100小时或更短时间换一次。
zh-Hans.consumables_filter_note:
注:
请用清水清洗，不要添加任何洗涤剂产品
请不要用刷子、手指直接清理滤网，以免损坏防水涂层
请务必晾晒干透后再使用(一般情况至少晾晒24小时)

en.consumables_main_brush_description: The main brush is the main cleaning part of the robot, and the main brush of the rubber body is rolled at high speed to roll the garbage into the dust box. However, as the working time increases, the main brush will wear out, which will affect the cleaning effect. It is recommended to change it once in 300 hours or less.
en.consumables_side_brush_description: The side brush is used to clean the corner garbage, and the garbage is fed into the main brush with the golden dip angle. However, as the working time increases, the brush will wear and affect the cleaning effect. It is recommended to change the work 200 hours or less.
en.consumables_filter_description: The washable filter is composed of high molecular fibers to prevent dust from escaping into the dust box. However, after working for a period of time, the filter may be blocked. It is recommended to wash it once every two weeks with water, and replace the filter for 150 hours or less.
en.consumables_mop_description: The mop is the main component of the robot entering the mopping mode. It is composed of microfiber, which has strong water absorption and high friction. However, as the working time increases and the cleaning is repeated, the fibers of the mop may wear or fall off, and it is recommended to change it once in 100 hours or less.
en.consumables_filter_note:
Note: 
Please wash with water, do not add any detergent products.
Please do not use brush or finger to clean the filter directly to avoid damage to the waterproof coating. 
Please be sure to dry and dry before use (usually at least 24 hours drying)
